Ripto (crypto) is a word that is quite phenomenal in investment, because it provides quite fantastic profits. The benefits provided reach hundreds or even thousands of percent in a short time.

Cryptocurrency is also called digital currency. This money can be transacted by fellow crypto users in a decentralized manner without going through a third party, using a sophisticated technology system called blockchain. The advantages of using this system are fast transaction times, no administration fees, and guaranteed security.

The value of cryptocurrencies fluctuates but tends to continue to strengthen, providing new potential profits for society. However, for beginners who are new to crypto, don't worry, because this book provides a variety of knowledge about cryptocurrencies along with how to trade and analyze them. This book can be read by all groups, especially people who welcome the presence of cryptocurrencies.
